03:39.360 --> 03:48.480
without necessarily finding the exit straight away. So this research does not descend from heaven

03:49.120 --> 03:56.960
that's really an absolutely crucial point so it's not like Moses coming down the mountain

03:56.960 --> 04:03.760
with God's words. It's really the result of inspiration, hard work, sweat and resilience.

04:04.560 --> 04:12.160
Resilience because things typically don't go right straight away and in fact any paper that

04:12.160 --> 04:19.520
you see published in a journal typically has been rejected one or twice, has been rewritten

04:19.520 --> 04:30.880
about 10 or 15 times and the amount of work that the authors put into it is hard to imagine when

04:30.880 --> 04:39.600
you see a nice neat little text that looks like a perfect finished product. Also it's important

04:39.600 --> 04:47.280
